<body>
<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1361411" n="1"/>
<opener>
<lb/><abbr>Illustriss.<hi rend="sup">o</hi></abbr> et <abbr>Celeber.<hi rend="sup">o</hi></abbr> Viro
               <lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Nicolao Bernoulli</rs>
<lb/><abbr>S. P. D.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-102552517" type="person">Petrus Antonius Michelotti</rs>
</opener>
<p>
<lb/>Novissim<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> quas accepi <rs key="B_991170515152605501" type="letter">liter<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs><note type="editorial">Brief von Johann I Bernoulli an Pietro Antonio Michelotti von 1718.04.09</note> Celeber. <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Patrui</rs> Tui occasio<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>nem mihi pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>bent ad Te scribendi Vir <abbr>Amiciss.<hi rend="sup">e</hi></abbr><supplied>.</supplied> Mitto
               <lb/>igitur occlusam <rs key="B_991170457446705501" type="letter">epistolam</rs><note type="editorial">Brief von Johann I Bernoulli an Nicolaus I Bernoulli von 1718.04.09</note> et eodem tempore respondeo cum
               <lb/>gratiarum actione ad tuas <rs key="B_991170517055905501" type="letter">literas</rs><note type="editorial">Brief von Nicolaus I Bernoulli an Pietro Antonio Michelotti von 1718.03.19</note> <date when="1718-03-19">19 transacti Martii</date> da<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tas. Optim<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> problematis solutionem dedisti in suppo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>sitione constantis<del> ingres</del> in canalem extensilem <subst><del>i</del><add>l</add></subst>i<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>quoris ingressus cum constanti velocitate. Optime etiam
               <lb/>dixisti quum te non intelligere fassus fuist<subst><del>e</del><add>i</add></subst> quomo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>do ista velocitati sanguinis arterias transcur<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>rentis applicari possint pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sertim quia in cordis di<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>latatione nulla fit Sanguinis in arterias a Corde
               <lb/>protrusio. H<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>c equidem vera sunt. Verum enimvero
               <lb/>tametsi in cordis dilatione sanguis non impellatur
               <lb/>in arterias, nihilo tamen se<unclear>c</unclear>ius haud sequitur cur<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>sum Sanguinis perire. Corde enim dilatato <choice><orig>Statim</orig><reg>statim</reg></choice>
<lb/>arteri<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> constringuntur cordisque, premendo san<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>guinem, supplent vices; et antequam arteri<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> con<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tract<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> depleantur Sanguine per eius cavitates
               <lb/>quaquaversum impetu a corde concepto et ab ar<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>teriarum contractione conservato, fluente pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>s<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>to est sanguis a corde (quod <choice><orig>Statim</orig><reg>statim</reg></choice> ac arteri<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> contrac<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>t<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> sunt constringitur contentumque in suo sinu san<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>guinem expellit) <choice><orig>Subministratus</orig><reg>subministratus</reg></choice>, qui arterias dilata<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<pb facs="1361412" n="2"/><lb break="no"/>re contendit. Quamobrem non male <abbr>Doctiss.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-11757645X" type="person">Gulielmi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>nus</rs> de <rs type="biblio">sanguinis natura et constitutione</rs> h<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>c scrip<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>sit. <cit type="long"><quote><choice><orig><g ref="#quote">„</g></orig><reg></reg></choice>Feriante (hoc est non sese constringente) igitur
               <lb/><choice><orig><g ref="#quote">„</g></orig><reg></reg></choice>corde non cessat, nec languet in suo cursu fluentum
               <lb/><choice><orig><g ref="#quote">„</g></orig><reg></reg></choice>sanguinis, sed perenni et uniformi agitatione
               <lb/><choice><orig><g ref="#quote">„</g></orig><reg></reg></choice>continu<choice><orig><g ref="#ograv">ò</g></orig><reg>o</reg></choice> et continenter sua vasa discurrit.</quote></cit>
</p>
<p>
               <lb/>In ordinem redigo <rs key="biblio_M3G2JA79" type="biblio">exercitationem</rs><note type="editorial">Vorstufe zu: Michelotti, Pietro Antonio, De separatione fluidorum in corpore animali dissertatio physico-mechanico-medica, Venetiis (Pinellorum <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>re) 1721</note> meam de separa<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tione Fluidorum in corpore Animali, et quam pri<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>mum ad Te mittam multa ad eius composi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tionem spectantia eum in finem ut sine ulla
               <lb/>adulatione ea consideres attente, moneasque
               <lb/>omnia qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> per inadvertentiam peccata commit<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tere potui <subst><del>eai</del><add>eadem ipsa</add></subst> benignitate tua corrigendo.
            </p>
<closer><salute>Vale
               <lb/>mihique ut assoles favere perge.</salute>
<lb/><dateline>Dabam <rs key="place_GEO-3164603" type="place">Venetiis</rs> <date when="1718-04-22"><abbr>a<supplied>.</supplied> d.</abbr> 22 Aprilis 1718</date><supplied>.</supplied></dateline><note hand="pers_DE-588-119166895"><foreign xml:lang="ger"><abbr>Empf.</abbr> den 23<hi rend="sup">ten</hi></foreign></note>
</closer>
<postscript>
<p>
<lb/><abbr>P. S<supplied>.</supplied></abbr>
<lb/>Perendie <abbr>Ill.<hi rend="sup">us</hi></abbr> et <abbr>Excell.<hi rend="sup">us</hi></abbr> <abbr>D.<hi rend="sup">us</hi></abbr> <choice><abbr>Proc.<hi rend="sup">r</hi></abbr><expan>Procurator</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-121843858" type="person">Theupolus</rs> erit istic
                  <lb/>ut apud nos quindecim circiter dies commoretur:
                  <lb/>quare te rogo atque hortor ut ipsum quotidie aliqua
                  <lb/>diei hora visites. Idem enim facient <abbr>D.<hi rend="sup">us</hi></abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-104265264" type="person">Morgagnus</rs>,
                  <pb facs="1361413" n="3"/>
<lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-118867865" type="person">Vallisnerius</rs> <abbr>etc.</abbr>
</p>
</postscript>
